{"tid":561222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"積犯非禮女途人 官：我知道你有輕度智障但唔係大晒","createTime":"2018-02-14T22:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T13:29:05.000Z","uid":145999,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dca4f7cf8b34e01db4bd2b5f585c06480a34b9d3","tid":561222,"uid":145999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T22:26:14.000Z","msg":"有12次風化案底的輕度智障的非禮案積犯，去年9月22日在黃大仙鳳德邨乘落單車期間，借勢摸身邊女途人的臀及大腿，被巡警目擊拘捕。積犯今承認非禮罪，裁判官表示：「我知道你有輕度智障，但唔係大晒，其他智障嘅人好守法。你吓吓見到女人就摸，根本係色情狂。人哋可唔可以見到邊個樣衰就揼邊個呀？人哋覺得睇你唔順眼，可唔可以揼你呀？唔得呀嘛。」最後提醒被告要守法，否則若他再犯案必定加刑，終判被告入獄3個月。<br />\n<br />\n被告楊楚康（19歲)，其精神科報告指他輕度弱智，但適合答辯。辯方求情指被告無業，靠父親的綜援過活。<br />\n<br />\n被告曾於2015年在升降機內非禮一名中六女生，事主作供時指因為被告「樣衰」所以印象深刻， 結果被告被裁定非禮罪成，被判入更生中心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180214/57832392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57832392&d=tC8wHLE06i9okBTfUkldoozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=58267655\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57832392&h=54580701\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180214/57832392</a><br />\n樣衰到比人認到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e618f4f5333150d008c0be3efa600658b38087a1","tid":561222,"uid":67815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T22:28:01.000Z","msg":"呢個可以同連登仔講"},{"pid":"f0074190a600ef3e3154bf2a6eabd537606e5651","tid":561222,"uid":17628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T22:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/064013_94c7b7a541ee48ec4fa50040e635409b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F064013_94c7b7a541ee48ec4fa50040e635409b.gif&h=c58173ef&s